<template>
  <Header title="Address Edit" />
  <van-address-edit
    :area-list="areaList"
    show-delete
    show-set-default
    :area-columns-placeholder="['请选择', '请选择', '请选择']"
    @save="onSave"
    @delete="onDelete"
  />
</template>

<script>
import { reactive, toRefs } from 'vue';
import Header from '../../components/Header.vue';
export default {
  components: { Header },
  setup() {
    let data = reactive({
      areaList: {
        province_list: {
          110000: 'VIC',
          120000: 'NSW',
        },
        city_list: {
          110100: 'Melbourne',
          110200: 'Wyndham',
          120100: 'Sydney',
          120200: 'Dubbo',
        },
        county_list: {
          110101: 'Melbourne Centre',
          110102: 'South Yarra',
          120102: 'Hawkesbury',
          130102: 'Frankston',
        },
      },
    });
    // save button
    const onSave = () => {};

    // delete button
    const onDelete = () => {};

    return {
      ...toRefs(data),
      onSave,
      onDelete,
    };
  },
};
</script>
<style>
    
</style>
<style lang='less' scoped>
    /deep/ .van-button--danger {
      background-color: #ffc400;

    }
    /deep/ .van-switch--on {
      background-color: #ffc400;
    }
    </style>
